Battleship Game

Objective:
Sink all the computer's ships before your own ships are sunk. 

Game Elements:
  Players board:
    Displays the players board, this is where the computer will be taking shots at
Computer Board:
    Displays the computers board, this is where the player will be choosing a spot to target

How to Play:
    Use arrow keys to move to a spot that you would like to target (there is no indicator telling you where you are)
    Press 'Enter' to fire at the selected position.
    X represents a hit, O is a miss, and . indicates unexplored space.
    The game alternates between player and computer turns.
    The computer's moves are automated.

Note:
    Ships are initially placed on the board
    The computer's moves are randomly generated using a simple AI i developed